{{see|nahuatl|náhuatl|Nàhuatl}}
==English==

===Etymology===
Spanish, from Nahuatl ''[[nahuatl]]'' / ''[[nahuatlatolli]]''.

===Noun===
'''Nahuatl'''

# The [[polysynthetic]] [[Aztecan]] language spoken by an indigenous people of [[Mexico]].

